  <content contentuid="hf1a2000000000098" version="1">剑意·初境</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a2000000000099" version="1">激活任一剑道流姿态时，武器攻击附加 1d6 对应元素伤害。</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000009a" version="1">剑意·进境</content>
