  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000009c" version="1">剑意·深境</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000009d" version="1">激活任一剑道流姿态时，武器攻击附加 1d10 对应元素伤害。</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000009e" version="1">剑意·化境</content>
