  <content contentuid="hf1a2000000000068" version="1">封符术充能（1）</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a2000000000069" version="1">获得 1 点封符术充能，长休后恢复。</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000006a" version="1">封符术充能（2）</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000006b" version="1">获得 2 点封符术充能，长休后恢复。</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000006c" version="1">封符术充能（4）</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000006d" version="1">获得 4 点封符术充能，长休后恢复。</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000006e" version="1">道法自然</content>
  <content contentuid="hf1a200000000006f" version="1">每次长休一次，可免费施展一个 8 环及以下自制法术，不消耗法术位。</content>
